OL,3,CMan paralysed for life forgives friend
OL,4,Cwho caused drink-drive crash
OL,6,FSam Blackledge reports on how Seth and
OL,7,FHarry were reunited after a horrific
OL,8,Fcrash
OL,10,FA man from Devon who was paralysed in
OL,11,Fa drink-driving crash says he has
OL,12,Fforgiven his best friend who was
OL,13,Fbehind the wheel that night.
OL,15,FSeth Marks, 21, suffered a spinal
OL,16,Finjury when his friend, Harry, ran
OL,17,Fthem off the road after an evening
OL,18,Fdrinking and taking drugs.
