OL,3,CMan paralysed for life forgives friend
OL,4,Cwho caused drink-drive crash
OL,6,FHarry was jailed, but following that,
OL,7,Fhe and Seth were able to meet and
OL,8,Freconcile through a restorative
OL,9,Fjustice scheme.
OL,11,FSeth says he doesn't recall what
OL,12,Fhappened on the night of the crash in
OL,13,F2022.
OL,15,F"I remember just meeting Harry in the
OL,16,Fpub, we were playing a few games of
OL,17,Fpool and we started drinking quite
OL,18,Fheavily", he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
