OL,3,CMan paralysed for life forgives friend
OL,4,Cwho caused drink-drive crash
OL,6,F"We started having some shots and
OL,7,Fthat's the last thing I remember."JThe
OL,8,Ffriends got into Harry's car for the
OL,9,Fshort journey home. But the vehicle
OL,10,Fsped off the road and collided with a
OL,11,Ffence.
OL,13,FSeth wasn't wearing a seatbelt and
OL,14,Fsuffered a broken neck and spine,
OL,15,Fleaving him paralysed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
