OL,3,CMan paralysed for life forgives friend
OL,4,Cwho caused drink-drive crash
OL,6,F"When I woke up I didn't have a clue
OL,7,Fwhat had happened to me," Seth said.
OL,8,F"I just wanted to talk to Harry. I had
OL,9,Fa lot of questions - why did we get
OL,10,Finto a car, why wasn't I wearing a
OL,11,Fseatbelt, how did I even end up in
OL,12,Fhospital?"
OL,14,FHarry was in prison, having been
OL,15,Farrested and charged with dangerous
OL,16,Fdriving.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
