OL,3,CMan paralysed for life forgives friend
OL,4,Cwho caused drink-drive crash
OL,6,FSeth was still recovering in hospital
OL,7,Fwhen the police offered him a chance
OL,8,Fto speak to his friend over a video
OL,9,Fcall.J"It was almost just like a catch-
OL,10,Fup," Seth said.
OL,12,F"He wanted to express how sorry he was
OL,13,Fto me, and I also just wanted to get
OL,14,Fsome clarity about the night and find
OL,15,Fout what had happened.
OL,17,F"It was a huge relief, it wasn't
OL,18,Fawkward between me and him, we just
OL,19,Fremained great friends."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
