OL,3,CMan paralysed for life forgives friend
OL,4,Cwho caused drink-drive crash
OL,6,FSeth's mum, Julie, also met with Harry
OL,7,Fwhile he was in prison.
OL,9,F"I was incredibly angry," Julie said.
OL,10,F"I didn't want an apology from him, it
OL,11,Fdoesn't matter how many times you say
OL,12,Fsorry, it's never going to rectify it.
OL,14,F"But I wanted him to take
OL,15,Fresponsibility, accountability, and
OL,16,Faccept what Seth's going through and
OL,17,Fwill go through for the rest of his
OL,18,Flife."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
