OL,3,CMan paralysed for life forgives friend
OL,4,Cwho caused drink-drive crash
OL,6,FSeth added: "I forgave him as soon as
OL,7,Fthe accident happened, I've never
OL,8,Fnever blamed him for my injuries, it
OL,9,Fwas all of us that made a very stupid
OL,10,Fdecision. Me and Harry have always
OL,11,Fbeen good mates and we always will be."
OL,13,FJax Baldock, from the Make Amends
OL,14,Fcharity which helped bring Seth and
OL,15,FHarry together again, said: "It's
OL,16,Fimportant that all victims of crime
OL,17,Fare made aware that they are entitled
OL,18,Fto restorative justice.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
