OL,3,CMan paralysed for life forgives friend
OL,4,Cwho caused drink-drive crash
OL,6,F"I would say to anybody who feels that
OL,7,Fmaybe restorative justice could help
OL,8,Fthem, look us up. Who knows, we might
OL,9,Fjust be able to help you to move on
OL,10,Ffrom whatever has happened to you."
OL,12,FAccording to national research,
OL,13,Frestorative justice can reduce
OL,14,Foffending by 14%
OL,16,FGovernment research shows that 85% of
OL,17,Fvictims who take part in the scheme
OL,18,Ffound the experience useful and were
OL,19,Fsatisfied with the outcome.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
