OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall Police and Crime
OL,7,FCommissioner Alison Hernandez said:
OL,8,F"Securing justice for victims is
OL,9,Fparamount to help them recover.
OL,11,F" I am in awe of the courage that some
OL,12,Fvictims are able to muster to engage
OL,13,Fin what can be a distressing, but
OL,14,Fconstructive conclusion to their crime.
