OL,6,F"Its aim is to help victims recover
OL,7,Fmore quickly, get answers to
OL,8,Fquestions, and crucially help
OL,9,Foffenders fully understand the
OL,10,Fdevastating impact their actions
OL,11,Fcaused in the hope of making it less
OL,12,Flikely they will offend again."
OL,14,FNon-crime and self-referrals to
OL,15,Fexplore restorative justice can be
OL,16,Fmade by emailing makeamends@shekinah.
OL,17,Fco.uk or calling 01803 222033.
